cted to read: &#x0201c;Hepatic VLDL<sub>1</sub>-triglyceride production rate was similar in the two groups at baseline: 411.0 &#x000b1; 49.5 vs. 437.2 &#x000b1; 32.4 mg/kg/day in responders vs. nonresponders.&#x0201d; <xref ref-type="fig" rid="F1">Figure 2<italic>C</italic></xref> also has been corrected (see new <xref ref-type="fig" rid="F1">Fig. 2<italic>C</italic></xref> below).</p><fig id="F1" fig-type="figure" orientation="portrait" position="float"><graphic xlink:href="dc18er06f1"/></fig><p>The online version of the article (<ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://doi.org/10.2337/dc15-1942">https://doi.org/10.2337/dc15-1942</ext-link>) reflects these changes.</p></body></article>